	    </li>
</ol><p>In the first example above, a stoichiometrically equivalent number of moles is <strong>one</strong> mole of <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow>
  <mtext mathcolor="red">\textcolor</mtext>
  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
