  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
    <mtext>BOH</mtext>
  </mrow>
</mrow><annotation encoding="math/tex">\textcolor{blue}{\text{BOH}}</annotation></semantics></math>. In the second example, a stoichiometrically equivalent number of moles is <strong>one</strong> mole of <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow>
  <mtext mathcolor="red">\textcolor</mtext>
  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
    <mi>r</mi>
    <mi>e</mi>
    <mi>d</mi>
  </mrow>
  <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
