</mrow><annotation encoding="math/tex">\textcolor{purple}{\textbf{KMnO}_{4}}</annotation></semantics></math>)</p><figure class="figure" title=""><img width="156" alt="Photo by iJammin on Flickr" draggable="false" src="photos/coppersulfatesolid.jpg"/></figure><p><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow>
